      • createLinphoneCore

        public abstract LinphoneCore createLinphoneCore(LinphoneCoreListener listener,
                                                java.lang.String userConfig,
                                                java.lang.String factoryConfig,
                                                java.lang.Object userdata,
                                                java.lang.Object context)
                                         throws LinphoneCoreException
        Create a LinphoneCore object. The LinphoneCore is the root for all liblinphone operations. You need only one per application.
        Parameters:
        listener - listener to receive notifications from the core
        userConfig - path where to read/write configuration (optional)
        factoryConfig - path where to read factory configuration (optional)
        userdata - any kind of application specific data
        context - an application context, on android this MUST be the android.content.Context object used by the application.
        Returns:
        a LinphoneCore object.
        Throws:
        LinphoneCoreException
